                        ●車がおすすめ（駐車場有）
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="syosaikokonoko">
                    <%= image_tag 'heart.jpg', class: 'syosaiheart' %>
                    <div class="syosaiheartbun">
                        豊かな自然の中で<br>モネを近くに感じる体験
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="migishita">
                <div class="syosaipointhidari">
                    <div class="syosaipoint">
                        <span class="dli-check-circle"><span></span></span>
                        <div class="syosaipointbun">
                        あの画家、モネが愛した庭がモデル
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="syosaipoint">
                        <span class="dli-check-circle"><span></span></span>
                        <div class="syosaipointbun">
                        四季折々の自然模様
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="syosaipointmigi">
                    <div class="syosaipoint">
                        <span class="dli-check-circle"><span></span></span>
                        <div class="syosaipointbun">
                        園内には３つの庭やカフェ、ショップなども
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="syosaipoint">
                        <span class="dli-check-circle"><span></span></span>
                        <div class="syosaipointbun">
                        自然の美しさを存分に味わって
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="subitem-container subitem-paused" ontouchstart="">  
